    FilterPluginsOfFamily
  </Paragraph>
  <Section Title="Description">
    <Paragraph>
      The <TypeRef>FilterPluginsOfFamily</TypeRef> method removes renderer plugins of the specified API family from the filtered set.
    </Paragraph>
  </Section>
  <Section Title="Usage">
    <Code Language="C++"><![CDATA[void FilterPluginsOfFamily(IRendererPlugin::ApiFamily apiFamily);]]></Code>
    <SubSection Title="Argument list">
      <ArgumentList>
        <ArgumentListEntry Type="ApiFamily!cobalt.graphics.IRendererPlugin.ApiFamily" Name="apiFamily">
          The API family to remove.
        </ArgumentListEntry>
      </ArgumentList>
    </SubSection>
  </Section>
